<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>pāmulapāṭi maṇḍanakuṁ baṁkkaruhānana yē 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ḍumāṁbakuṁ gāmanibhuṁḍu gommana 
<lb n="3"/>nukhasthitiṁ buṭṭi nijānvavāyanutrā 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>muṁḍu dallidaṁḍrulaku dharmmuvugāṁ da 
<lb n="5" break="no"/>navṛttipai grahagrāmaṇiṁ bōla dīpaka ma 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>khaṇḍita maimahiṁ barvviyoppaṁ gānu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">1</supplied> sara 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>dhinidhikhēṁddhu sakavatsarasaṁkhyalaṁ gārttika<unclear>mu</unclear> 
<lb n="8" break="no"/>na davalimapūrnnasthiraguru dinamunaṁ gomma 
<lb n="9" break="no"/>na yurutaradīpaṁbu śivuna koppaṁga nilpenu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">2</supplied> komma 
<lb n="10" break="no"/>na damatallidaṁḍrulaku dharmmārtthaṁbugā nakha 
<lb n="11" break="no"/>ṇḍadīpaṁbunakuṁ beṭṭina goṟiyalu 55 vīniṁ 
<lb n="12"/>jēkoni mrānubōyu koḍku vēme 
<lb n="13"/>danaputrapautrānikamu nitya 
<lb n="14"/>māneṁḍu neyi vōyaṁgalavā 
<lb n="15" break="no"/><unclear>ṁḍu</unclear> 
</p>

